    <title>一.汇编概述</title>
    <url>/2021/04/14/01.%E6%B1%87%E7%BC%96%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p> 汇编语言</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="0x1-概述"><a href="#0x1-概述" class="headerlink" title="0x1.概述"></a>0x1.概述</h3><p><strong>推荐书籍：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/26769528/">汇编语言：基于x86处理器</a></li>
</ul>
<p>汇编语言3大组成部分</p>
<ul>
<li>寄存器</li>
<li>指令</li>
<li>内存</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="0x2-环境搭建"><a href="#0x2-环境搭建" class="headerlink" title="0x2.环境搭建"></a>0x2.环境搭建</h3><ul>
<li>下载  <a href="http://www.masm32.com/">masm32</a> 环境</li>
<li>配置 VS2017 汇编环境</li>
</ul>
<p>新建一个空项目，新建一个<code>.asm</code>文件，之后右键项目名，在弹出的菜单中选择<code>生成依赖项</code>–&gt;<code>生成自定义</code>–&gt;<code>masm</code></p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414041946695.png" alt="image-20210414041946695"></p>
<p>①配置<code>include</code>路径：<code>Microsoft Macro Assembler</code>–&gt;<code>General</code>–&gt;<code>Inlude Paths</code>–&gt;勾选从父文件夹继承，设置路径<code>D:\APPS\Env\masm32\include</code></p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414042200330.png" alt="image-20210414042200330"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>注意：如果项目设置中没看到<code>Microsoft Macro Assembler</code>选项，删除<code>.asm</code>文件，重新创建。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>②配置<code>lib</code>路径：<code>链接器</code>–&gt;<code>常规</code>–&gt;<code>附加库目录</code>–&gt;设置路径 <code>D:\APPS\Env\masm32\lib</code></p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414042140742.png" alt="image-20210414042140742"></p>
<ul>
<li>编写测试程序：</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.586 ; 指令集</span><br><span class="line">.model flat, stdcall ; 内存使用模式flat， stdcall 调用约定</span><br><span class="line">option casemap:none</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">include windows.inc ; 类似于包含头文件</span><br><span class="line">include user32.inc</span><br><span class="line">include kernel32.inc</span><br><span class="line">includelib user32.lib ; 链接库</span><br><span class="line">includelib kernel32.lib</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.data</span><br><span class="line">text db &quot;HelloWorld&quot;, 0</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.code</span><br><span class="line">main proc ; proc 函数的意思, main 入口点，自己指定的</span><br><span class="line">	invoke MessageBox, 0, offset text, 0, 0</span><br><span class="line">	invoke ExitProcess, 0</span><br><span class="line">main endp</span><br><span class="line">end main ; main 是一个标号，END main 是告诉编译器，起始位置在哪</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>运行效果：</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414042355367.png" alt="image-20210414042355367"></p>
<h3 id="0x3-总结"><a href="#0x3-总结" class="headerlink" title="0x3.总结"></a>0x3.总结</h3><blockquote>
<p>VS搭建汇编环境步骤</p>
<ol>
<li>下载<code>masm32</code></li>
<li>VS创建空项目，并创建<code>.asm</code>文件</li>
<li>修改项目项目依赖项–&gt;生成自定义–&gt;<code>选择masm</code></li>
<li>配置项目属性</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>链接–&gt;常规–&gt;附加库目录: <code>D:\APPS\Env\masm32\lib</code></li>
<li>Microsoft Macro Assembler–&gt;General–&gt;Inlude Paths: <code>D:\APPS\Env\masm32\include</code></li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>汇编</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>汇编</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
