  <entry>
    <title>IDA动态调试ELF文件</title>
    <url>/2021/04/12/IDA%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95ELF%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>IDA动态调试ELF文件</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="IDA动态调试ELF文件"><a href="#IDA动态调试ELF文件" class="headerlink" title="IDA动态调试ELF文件"></a>IDA动态调试ELF文件</h2><ul>
<li>找到<code>IDA根目录</code>，复制<code>linux_server</code>到<code>linux</code>系统中</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">32</span>位: IDA目录\dbgsrv\linux_server</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">64</span>位: IDA目录\dbgsrv\linux_server64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>在<code>linux</code>中，进入<code>linux_server</code>所在目录，给<code>linux_server</code>赋予可执行权限</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ chmod +x linux_server64</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>启动linux_server</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> ./linux_server64</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>在<code>windows</code>端打开对应版本<code>IDA</code>，菜单栏中<code>Debugger--&gt;Run--&gt;Romote Linux debugger</code></li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/04/12/jXTlWQ9k1G5wnyJ.png" alt="image-20210412235436807"></p>
<blockquote>
<pre>
Application: 要调试程序路径
Directory: 存放呗调试程序的路径
Hostname：linux主机的ip地址
其它默认
</pre>
</blockquote>
<p>ok即可进入<code>IDA</code>动态调试。</p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>IDA</tag>
        <tag>病毒分析</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>NexT主题优化</title>
    <url>/2021/04/14/NexT%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>NexT主题优化</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h4 id="添加站内搜索功能"><a href="#添加站内搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="添加站内搜索功能"></a>添加站内搜索功能</h4><ol>
<li>下载插件</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; npm install hexo<span class="literal">-generator</span><span class="literal">-searchdb</span> -<span class="literal">-save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="2">
<li>配置站点配置文件<code>E:\code\blog\_config.yml</code>，新增以下内容到任意位置：</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">format:</span> <span class="string">html</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">limit:</span> <span class="number">10000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="3">
<li>编辑主题配置文件<code>E:\code\blog\themes\next\_config.yml</code>，搜索：<code>local_search</code>，将 enable的 <code>false</code>改为<code>true</code></li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Local Search</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Dependencies: https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-generator-searchdb</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">local_search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果：</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414002616875.png" alt="image-20210414002616875"></p>
<h4 id="添加评论系统"><a href="#添加评论系统" class="headerlink" title="添加评论系统"></a>添加评论系统</h4><ol>
<li>注册<a href="https://www.leancloud.cn/">LeanClound</a>，获取<code>APP ID</code>和<code>APP Key</code>。</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>注册成功后，创建应用，<code>开发版</code>，<code>名称</code>和<code>描述</code>自定义，之后进入该应用设置，在<code>侧边菜单栏</code>选中<code>数据存储</code>–&gt;<code>结构化数据</code>–&gt;<code>创建Class</code>：</li>
</ul>
<p>新建<code>Comment</code>和<code>Counter</code>（这个是用于记录文章阅读量统计），其中权限为<code>无限制</code></p>
<blockquote>
<p>说明：<code>Comment</code>和<code>Counter</code>默认不创建会自动创建。</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><code>侧边栏</code>选中<code>设置</code>–&gt;<code>安全中心</code>–&gt;只打开<code>数据存储</code>，<code>其余全部关闭</code></li>
<li><code>侧边栏</code>选中<code>设置</code>–&gt;<code>应用Keys</code>–&gt;记录<code>AppID</code>和<code>AppKey</code>到<code>NexT</code>，后面会用。</li>
</ul>
<ol start="2">
<li>在博客中设置评论系统</li>
</ol>
<p>获取最新的 <a href="https://valine.js.org/">valine.min.js</a> 的cdn地址</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414013916501.png" alt="image-20210414013916501"></p>
<p>修改主题配置文件<code>E:\code\blog\themes\next\_config.yml</code>，搜索<code>valine</code>找到如下位置配置<code>CDN</code>：</p>
<p><img src="https://gitee.com/rkhorse/blogimgs/raw/master/imgs/image-20210414014038761.png" alt="image-20210414014038761"></p>
<p>之后再次搜索<code>valine</code>配置其参数：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Valine</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># For more information: https://valine.js.org, https://github.com/xCss/Valine</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">valine:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">appid:</span>  <span class="comment"># Your leancloud application appid，填写注册LearnCloud中 appid</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">appkey:</span> <span class="comment"># Your leancloud application appkey, 填写注册LearnCloud中appkey</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">notify:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment"># Mail notifier</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">verify:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment"># Verification code</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">placeholder:</span> <span class="string">欢迎畅所欲言</span> <span class="comment"># Comment box placeholder</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">avatar:</span> <span class="string">mm</span> <span class="comment"># Gravatar style</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">guest_info:</span> <span class="string">nick,mail,link</span> <span class="comment"># Custom comment header</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">pageSize:</span> <span class="number">10</span> <span class="comment"># Pagination size</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zn-ch</span> <span class="comment"># Language, available values: en, zh-cn</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">visitor:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># Article reading statistic</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">comment_count:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># If false, comment count will only be displayed in post page, not in home page</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">recordIP:</span> <span class="literal">true</span> <span class="comment"># Whether to record the commenter IP</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">serverURLs:</span> <span class="comment"># When the custom domain name is enabled, fill it in here (it will be detected automatically by default, no need to fill in)</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#post_meta_order: 0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h5 id="评论用户头像配置"><a href="#评论用户头像配置" class="headerlink" title="评论用户头像配置"></a>评论用户头像配置</h5><p>参考文档：<a href="https://valine.js.org/avatar.html">https://valine.js.org/avatar.html</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>PS：关闭指定文章的评论功能：</p>
<p>在对应<code>markdown</code>文件中头部添加<code>comments: false</code></p>
<figure class="highlight vbnet"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">title:</span> 标签</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">type:</span> <span class="string">&quot;tags&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">comments:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</blockquote>
<h4 id="站点底部添加访问量"><a href="#站点底部添加访问量" class="headerlink" title="站点底部添加访问量"></a>站点底部添加访问量</h4><p>编辑<code>E:\code\blog\themes\next\layout\_partials\footer.swig</code>，搜索<code>copyright</code>，在其上方添加：</p>
<figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script async src=&quot;https://busuanzi.ibruce.info/busuanzi/2.3/busuanzi.pure.mini.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="文章置顶"><a href="#文章置顶" class="headerlink" title="文章置顶"></a>文章置顶</h4><ol>
<li>安装插件</li>
</ol>
<p>在站点目录<code>E:</code>打开终端：</p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; npm uninstall hexo<span class="literal">-generator</span><span class="literal">-index</span> -<span class="literal">-save</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; npm install hexo<span class="literal">-generator</span><span class="literal">-index</span><span class="literal">-pin</span><span class="literal">-top</span> -<span class="literal">-save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="2">
<li>在需要置顶的文章的<code>Front-matter</code>中加上<code>top: true</code></li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight nsis"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="literal">top</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果：</p>
<p><strong>参考文档</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://valine.js.org/">Valine</a></p>
<p><a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/third-party-services.html#local-search">站内搜索</a></p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>博客搭建</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>NexT</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
