  <entry>
    <title>Hexo+Gitee搭建个人博客</title>
    <url>/2021/04/12/hexo+gitee%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>利用Hexo+gitee搭建个人博客</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="0x1-hexo"><a href="#0x1-hexo" class="headerlink" title="0x1 hexo"></a>0x1 hexo</h3><ul>
<li>安装node.js</li>
<li>安装git</li>
<li>新建文件夹<code>E:\code\blog</code>，打开终端</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; hexo init</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; hexo g</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>其中<code>hexo init</code>为安装<code>hexo</code>环境，<code>hexo g</code>生成静态页面，<code>hexo s</code>启动hexo服务。</p>
<p>之后在浏览器验证：<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a></p>
<h3 id="0x2-安装hexo主题"><a href="#0x2-安装hexo主题" class="headerlink" title="0x2 安装hexo主题"></a>0x2 安装hexo主题</h3><ul>
<li>安装<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">next主题</a></li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; git clone https://github.com/theme<span class="literal">-next</span>/hexo<span class="literal">-theme</span><span class="literal">-next</span> themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>更新</li>
</ul>
<p>NexT 每个月都会发布新版本。你可以通过如下命令更新到最新的 master 分支：</p>
<figure class="highlight taggerscript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PS E:<span class="symbol">\c</span>ode<span class="symbol">\b</span>log&gt; cd themes/next</span><br><span class="line">PS E:<span class="symbol">\c</span>ode<span class="symbol">\b</span>log<span class="symbol">\t</span>hemes/next&gt; git pull</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>安装swig组件</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; npm i hexo<span class="literal">-renderer</span><span class="literal">-swig</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>说明：在hexo在5.0之后把swig给删除了，所以需要自己手动安装</p>
<ul>
<li>修改hexo配置文件：<code>E:\code\blog\_config.yml</code></li>
</ul>
<p>搜索<code>theme:</code>，修改为<code>theme: next</code></p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>验证主题</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; hexo g</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; hexo s <span class="literal">-debug</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>之后在浏览器中验证：<a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000</a></p>
<ul>
<li>优化主题：具体查看<a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/">NexT使用手册</a></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="0x3-部署Gitee"><a href="#0x3-部署Gitee" class="headerlink" title="0x3 部署Gitee"></a>0x3 部署Gitee</h3><ul>
<li>申请gitee账号</li>
<li>新建仓库</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight makefile"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">仓库名称: blog</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">路径: 和用户名一样</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">是否开源: 公开</span></span><br><span class="line">其他默认</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>配置ssh密钥</li>
</ul>
<p>进入设置–&gt;安全设置–&gt;SSH公钥</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/04/12/NmjPqQFAod9HRhZ.png" alt="image-20210412084510245"></p>
<p>简单的说就是，在命令行中：</p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>进入创建后的仓库–&gt;服务–&gt;Gitee Pages</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/04/12/mA14N7L9FYykIED.png" alt="image-20210412084118636"></p>
<p>可以看到自己搭建blog网站地址：</p>
<p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/04/12/u6R7e95ftwKHBCJ.png" alt="image-20210412084311593"></p>
<h3 id="0x4-开始部署"><a href="#0x4-开始部署" class="headerlink" title="0x4 开始部署"></a>0x4 开始部署</h3><h4 id="0x4-1-本地部署"><a href="#0x4-1-本地部署" class="headerlink" title="0x4.1 本地部署"></a>0x4.1 本地部署</h4><p>在<code>主题根目录</code>打开终端：</p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; hexo g; hexo s;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>之后打开：<a href="http://localhost:4000/%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F">http://localhost:4000/验证是否部署成功</a></p>
<h4 id="0x4-2-部署到Gitee和GitHub"><a href="#0x4-2-部署到Gitee和GitHub" class="headerlink" title="0x4.2 部署到Gitee和GitHub"></a>0x4.2 部署到Gitee和GitHub</h4><ol>
<li>安装部署插件</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; npm install hexo<span class="literal">-deployer</span><span class="literal">-git</span> -<span class="literal">-save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="2">
<li>修改部署配置</li>
</ol>
<p>复制刚刚创建的仓库地址：</p>
<ul>
<li><p><code>https</code>：部署需要账户密码。</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>ssh</code>：部署不需要密码，但需要先配置一下<code>ssh key</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>在站点配置文件 <code>E:\code\blog\_config.yml</code> 中修改参数：</p>
<figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  type:</span> git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  repo:</span> git@github.com:rkhorse/rkhorse.github.io.git <span class="meta"># 仓库地址</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  branch:</span> master <span class="meta"># 部署分支</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>注意：部署分支要和我们远端仓库的部署分支对应，没设置的话<code>Hexo</code>会自动创建一个分支作为部署分支。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>同时部署到<code>Github</code>和<code>Gitee</code>的<code>deploy参数</code>配置：</p>
<figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  type:</span> git</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  repo:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta"># 部署到github  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">    github:</span> git@github.com:rkhorse/rkhorse.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta"># 部署到gitee</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">    gitee:</span> https:<span class="comment">//gitee.com/rkhorse/rkhorse.git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">  branch:</span> master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ol start="3">
<li>执行<code>部署命令</code></li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">PS</span> E:\code\blog&gt; hexo clean; hexo g; hexo d;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="0x5-参考文档"><a href="#0x5-参考文档" class="headerlink" title="0x5 参考文档"></a>0x5 参考文档</h3><ul>
<li>hexo 官网：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
